<subSubSection id="99F2651FFFB4FFEEFF1CFE3B4BA1FD35" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="D1573694FFB4FFEEFF1CFE3B4B89FDB5" blockId="5.[113,763,492,708]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB4FFEEFF1CFE3B4989FDF5" box="[151,235,493,516]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">Notes. –</emphasis>
In the protologue, 
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB4FFEEFE4DFE3A4BCBFDF5" author="BURMAN" box="[454,681,492,516]" firstAuthor="BURMAN" journalOrPublisher="Amsterdam" page="228" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" refId="ref8940" refString="BURMAN, N. L. (1768). Flora Indica: cui accedit series zoophytorum indicorum, nec non prodromus florae capensis. Amsterdam." title="Flora Indica: cui accedit series zoophytorum indicorum, nec non prodromus florae capensis" type="book" year="1768">BURMAN (1768: 228)</bibRefCitation>
cited a 
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB4FFEEFFFAFDDB49D3FDD5" box="[113,177,525,548]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">Pryon</emphasis>
specimen and two illustrations (
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB4FFEEFDABFDDA4B99FDD5" author="RUMPHIUS, G. E." box="[544,763,524,548]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" refId="ref10148" refString="RUMPHIUS, G. E. [BURMAN, J. (ed.)] (1741 - 1750). Herbarium Amboinense. 6 vol. Amsterdam, The Hague, Utrecht. [vol. 6, 1750]" type="book" year="1750">RUMPHIUS, 1750: 75</bibRefCitation>
(
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB4FFEEFFF1FDFA49ABFDB5" box="[122,201,556,580]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">sphalm.</emphasis>
“76”), tab. 33; 
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB4FFEEFED5FDFB4895FDB5" author="PETIVER" box="[350,503,556,580]" firstAuthor="PETIVER" journalOrPublisher="London" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" refId="ref10041" refString="PETIVER J. (1702 - 1709). Gazophylaciis naturae &amp; artis decades. London." title="Gazophylaciis naturae &amp; artis decades" type="book" year="1702">PETIVER, 1702</bibRefCitation>
– 1709: tab. 64, fig. 10).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D1573694FFB4FFEEFF1CFD9A4BA1FD35" blockId="5.[113,763,492,708]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">
<bibRefCitation id="B5794B65FFB4FFEEFF1CFD9A48F6FD95" author="HOLTTUM" box="[151,404,588,612]" firstAuthor="HOLTTUM" journalOrPublisher="Fl. Males." page="59" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" pagination="37 - 61" part="1" refId="ref9475" refString="HOLTTUM, R. E. (1959 a). Schizaeaceae. Fl. Males. ser. 2, 1: 37 - 61." title="Schizaeaceae" type="journal article" year="1959" yearSuffix="a">HOLTTUM (1959a: 59)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned as 
<typeStatus id="0E538836FFB4FFEEFDCAFD9B4B10FD94" box="[577,626,589,613]" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">type</typeStatus>
“ 
<collectingRegion id="132CF876FFB4FFEEFD0EFD9A4BD4FD95" box="[645,694,588,612]" country="Indonesia" name="Jawa Timur" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">Java</collectingRegion>
, herb. Burman (
<collectionCode id="B7F9AE51FFB4FFEEFF6BFDBA499AFD75" box="[224,248,620,644]" country="Switzerland" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15706" name="Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques de la Ville de Genève" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" type="Herbarium">G</collectionCode>
, not seen)”. As the only original material in G-PREL is a 
<emphasis id="E39CEA86FFB4FFEEFE8CFD5B4827FD55" box="[263,325,653,676]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">Pryon</emphasis>
collection from 
<collectingRegion id="132CF876FFB4FFEEFE79FD5B4B7FFD55" box="[498,541,653,676]" country="Indonesia" name="Jawa Timur" pageId="5" pageNumber="98">Java</collectingRegion>
[
<collectionCode id="B7F9AE51FFB4FFEEFDA1FD5A4B5CFD55" box="[554,574,652,676]" country="Switzerland" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15706" name="Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques de la Ville de Genève" pageId="5" pageNumber="98" type="Herbarium">G</collectionCode>
00818001], Holttum’s statement is accepted as implicit lectotypification.
</paragraph>
